Well, I do love Chinese food.

1522
00:58:05,014 --> 00:58:07,517
-Also, I recently visited Hong Kong.
-I see.

1523
00:58:07,584 --> 00:58:09,419
I often interact with restaurants there,

1524
00:58:09,486 --> 00:58:11,287
