1541
00:58:48,391 --> 00:58:50,260
Shallots, button mushrooms,

1542
00:58:50,326 --> 00:58:51,995
-rosemary, and others.
-"Shallots."

1543
00:58:52,061 --> 00:58:54,297
-Butter.
-She's not any different.

1544
00:58:54,364 --> 00:58:55,832
Also, just before

1545
00:58:55,899 --> 00:58:57,534
I opened my restaurant,

1546
