Jong-won taught me how to make tuile.

1547
00:58:59,602 --> 00:59:01,070
I went to his restaurant and learned.

1548
00:59:01,137 --> 00:59:03,172
-I see.
-You studied there.

1549
00:59:03,239 --> 00:59:06,643
So I'll even make tuile
and cook like a Parisienne

1550
00:59:06,709 --> 00:59:09,479
