1553
00:59:13,683 --> 00:59:14,951
Well, I'll have to boil stuff.

1554
00:59:15,251 --> 00:59:17,654
CAN'T HIDE HER CRAZY SOUL

1555
00:59:17,720 --> 00:59:20,089
