in front of Jong-won?

1557
00:59:22,392 --> 00:59:24,661
-Take a look.
-Is that Poong's knife?

1558
00:59:24,727 --> 00:59:26,362
Poong has

1559
00:59:26,863 --> 00:59:29,699
