1560
00:59:29,766 --> 00:59:33,102
So I decided to borrow this
to break that curse for him.

1561
00:59:33,369 --> 00:59:35,271
HOW SWEET YOU ARE

1562
00:59:35,338 --> 00:59:39,342
Will he be able to beat Eun-yeong
with Poong's knife?

1563
00:59:39,409 --> 00:59:40,610
It won't be easy.

1564
00:59:41,544 --> 00:59:43,546
CHEF EUN-YEONG'S INGREDIENTS:
BUTTON MUSHROOM, SHALLOT, CAVIAR

1565
