-What is it?

1590
01:00:44,807 --> 01:00:46,075
Park Eun-yeong!

1591
01:00:46,142 --> 01:00:48,177
HE CALLED ON EUN-YEONG?

1592
01:00:48,511 --> 01:00:51,814
EVERYONE'S ANTICIPATION GOES UP

1593
01:00:52,815 --> 01:00:54,117
Park Eun-yeong!

1594
01:00:54,183 --> 01:00:55,485
