1595
01:00:55,551 --> 01:00:57,320
STRIKEOUT

1596
01:00:57,620 --> 01:01:00,323
THEY DEFINITELY SWAPPED THEIR BODIES

1597
01:01:00,923 --> 01:01:02,191
DROP…

1598
01:01:02,425 --> 01:01:03,559
BACK TO HIS INFP SELF

