1602
01:01:13,703 --> 01:01:15,805
NOT EASY TO RECOVER FROM

1603
01:01:15,872 --> 01:01:17,707
You'll be promoted to an executive soon!

1604
01:01:18,007 --> 01:01:19,509
HAVING A MILLION THOUGHTS

1605
01:01:19,575 --> 01:01:22,145
